longBusinessSummary: EnGold Mines Ltd. explores and evaluates mineral properties in Canada. The company explores for gold, copper, and silver deposits. It holds 100% interest in the Lac La Hache property covering an area of 25,750 hectares located in the Cariboo region of central British Columbia, Canada. The company was formerly known as GWR Resources Inc. and changed its name to Engold Mines Limited in May 2016. EnGold Mines Ltd. is based in Vancouver, Canada.
